display_name: QuantityConversion - 00. SAP S/4 HANA Extraction Pool_S4H-HANA

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT DISTINCT 
    <%=sourceSystem%>  || '::' || 
        CASE
            WHEN "T006"."DIMID" != 'AAAADL'
            THEN "MARA"."MANDT" || '::' || "MARA"."MATNR" || '::' || "MARA"."MEINS" || '::' || "T006D"."MSSIE"
            WHEN "T006"."DIMID" = 'AAAADL'
            THEN "MARA"."MANDT" || '::' || "MARA"."MATNR" || '::' || "MARA"."MEINS" || '::' || "MARM"."MEINH"
        END                                                    AS "ID",
       "MARA"."MATNR"                                          AS "MaterialNumber",
       "MARA"."MATNR"                                          AS "ConversionQualifier",
       "MARA"."MEINS"                                          AS "FromUnit",
       CASE
           WHEN "T006"."DIMID" != 'AAAADL'
               THEN "T006D"."MSSIE"
           WHEN "T006"."DIMID" = 'AAAADL'
               THEN "MARM"."MEINH"
           END                                                 AS "ToUnit",
       CASE
           WHEN "T006"."DIMID" != 'AAAADL'
               THEN "T006"."ZAEHL" / "T006"."NENNR" * POWER(10, "T006"."EXP10")
           WHEN "T006"."DIMID" = 'AAAADL'
               THEN "MARM"."UMREN" / "MARM"."UMREZ"
           END                                                 AS "Rate",
       <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "MARA"."MANDT"             AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "MARA" AS "MARA"
    LEFT JOIN "T006" AS "T006"
        ON "MARA"."MANDT" = "T006"."MANDT"
            AND "MARA"."MEINS" = "T006"."MSEHI"
    LEFT JOIN "T006D" AS "T006D"
        ON "T006"."MANDT" = "T006D"."MANDT"
            AND "T006"."DIMID" = "T006D"."DIMID"
    LEFT JOIN "MARM" AS "MARM"
        ON "MARA"."MANDT" = "MARM"."MANDT"
            AND "MARA"."MATNR" = "MARM"."MATNR"
WHERE NULLIF("T006"."MANDT", '') IS NOT NULL
  AND NULLIF("MARM"."MANDT", '') IS NOT NULL

WITH "CTE_CONVERSION" AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
        "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."ItemBasePEOOrganizationId"    AS "ItemBasePEOOrganizationId",
        "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."ItemBasePEOInventoryItemId"   AS "ItemBasePEOInventoryItemId",
        "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS"."ToUomCode"             AS "TO_UOM_CODE",
        "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS"."FromUomCode"           AS "FROM_UOM_CODE",
        "ItemUOMConversionPVO"."ConversionRate"             AS "ConversionRate"
    FROM "FscmTopModelAM_InvUomPublicViewAM_UOMIntraClassPVO" AS "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS"
        LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_ScmExtractAM_ScmRcsBiccExtractAM_ItemUOMConversionPVO" AS "ItemUOMConversionPVO"
            ON "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS"."InventoryItemId" = "ItemUOMConversionPVO"."InventoryItemId"
        LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_ScmExtractAM_EgpBiccExtractAM_ItemExtractPVO" AS "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"
            ON "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS"."InventoryItemId" = "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."ItemBasePEOInventoryItemId"
)
SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "CONVERSION"."ItemBasePEOOrganizationId" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."ItemBasePEOInventoryItemId" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."FROM_UOM_CODE" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."TO_UOM_CODE"  
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."ConversionRate"                             AS "ID",
    "CONVERSION"."ItemBasePEOOrganizationId" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."ItemBasePEOInventoryItemId"                 AS "MaterialNumber",
    "CONVERSION"."ItemBasePEOOrganizationId" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."ItemBasePEOInventoryItemId"                 AS "ConversionQualifier",
    "CONVERSION"."FROM_UOM_CODE"                                         AS "FromUnit",
    "CONVERSION"."TO_UOM_CODE"                                           AS "ToUnit",
    "CONVERSION"."ConversionRate"                                        AS "Rate",
    <%=sourceSystem%>                                                    AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "CTE_CONVERSION" AS "CONVERSION"

SELECT DISTINCT 
    <%=sourceSystem%>  || '::' || 
        CASE
            WHEN "T006"."DIMID" != 'AAAADL'
            THEN "MARA"."MANDT" || '::' || "MARA"."MATNR" || '::' || "MARA"."MEINS" || '::' || "T006D"."MSSIE"
            WHEN "T006"."DIMID" = 'AAAADL'
            THEN "MARA"."MANDT" || '::' || "MARA"."MATNR" || '::' || "MARA"."MEINS" || '::' || "MARM"."MEINH"
        END                                                    AS "ID",
       "MARA"."MATNR"                                          AS "MaterialNumber",
       "MARA"."MATNR"                                          AS "ConversionQualifier",
       "MARA"."MEINS"                                          AS "FromUnit",
       CASE
           WHEN "T006"."DIMID" != 'AAAADL'
               THEN "T006D"."MSSIE"
           WHEN "T006"."DIMID" = 'AAAADL'
               THEN "MARM"."MEINH"
           END                                                 AS "ToUnit",
       CASE
           WHEN "T006"."DIMID" != 'AAAADL'
               THEN "T006"."ZAEHL" / "T006"."NENNR" * POWER(10, "T006"."EXP10")
           WHEN "T006"."DIMID" = 'AAAADL'
               THEN "MARM"."UMREN" / "MARM"."UMREZ"
           END                                                 AS "Rate",
       <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "MARA"."MANDT"             AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "MARA" AS "MARA"
    LEFT JOIN "T006" AS "T006"
        ON "MARA"."MANDT" = "T006"."MANDT"
            AND "MARA"."MEINS" = "T006"."MSEHI"
    LEFT JOIN "T006D" AS "T006D"
        ON "T006"."MANDT" = "T006D"."MANDT"
            AND "T006"."DIMID" = "T006D"."DIMID"
    LEFT JOIN "MARM" AS "MARM"
        ON "MARA"."MANDT" = "MARM"."MANDT"
            AND "MARA"."MATNR" = "MARM"."MATNR"
WHERE NULLIF("T006"."MANDT", '') IS NOT NULL
  AND NULLIF("MARM"."MANDT", '') IS NOT NULL

WITH "CTE_CONVERSION" AS (
    SELECT
        "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."ORGANIZATION_ID",
        "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID",
        "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS"."TO_UOM_CODE"       AS "FROM_UOM_CODE",
        "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS"."FROM_UOM_CODE"     AS "TO_UOM_CODE",
        "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS"."CONVERSION_RATE"
    FROM "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS" AS "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS",
        "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B" AS "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"
    WHERE "MTL_UOM_CLASS_CONVERSIONS"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID" = "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID"
    UNION ALL
    SELECT
        "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."ORGANIZATION_ID",
        "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID",
        "MTL_UNITS_OF_MEASURE_TL"."UOM_CODE"            AS "FROM_UOM_CODE",
        "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."PRIMARY_UOM_CODE"         AS "TO_UOM_CODE",
        1 / "MTL_UOM_CONVERSIONS"."CONVERSION_RATE"
    FROM "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B" AS "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B",
        "MTL_UOM_CONVERSIONS" AS "MTL_UOM_CONVERSIONS",
        "MTL_UNITS_OF_MEASURE_TL" AS "MTL_UNITS_OF_MEASURE_TL"
    WHERE "MTL_SYSTEM_ITEMS_B"."PRIMARY_UOM_CODE" = "MTL_UOM_CONVERSIONS"."UOM_CODE"
        AND "MTL_UOM_CONVERSIONS"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID" = 0
        AND "MTL_UOM_CONVERSIONS"."UOM_CLASS" = "MTL_UNITS_OF_MEASURE_TL"."UOM_CLASS"
        AND "MTL_UNITS_OF_MEASURE_TL"."BASE_UOM_FLAG" = 'Y'
        AND "MTL_UNITS_OF_MEASURE_TL"."LANGUAGE" = <%=LanguageKey%>
)
SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "CONVERSION"."ORGANIZATION_ID" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."FROM_UOM_CODE" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."TO_UOM_CODE"        AS "ID",
    "CONVERSION"."ORGANIZATION_ID" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID"  AS "MaterialNumber",
    "CONVERSION"."ORGANIZATION_ID" 
    || '::' || "CONVERSION"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID"  AS "ConversionQualifier",
    "CONVERSION"."FROM_UOM_CODE"                 AS "FromUnit",
    "CONVERSION"."TO_UOM_CODE"                   AS "ToUnit",
    "CONVERSION"."CONVERSION_RATE"               AS "Rate",
    <%=sourceSystem%>                            AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM
    "CTE_CONVERSION" AS "CONVERSION"
